snippet.title: IMPETUS - Clamor in portis
snippet.description:
This is IMPETUS, a tactical turn-based game set in the era after the Fall of the Roman Empire (4th-5th century AD).

Each player (PvP) will command a legion composed of several units, each of which has its own stats in terms of movement, attack, attack range, defense.
